thread.title: Chris Howell
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Chris Howell

author: Chris Howell
title: Chris Howell
text:
Not over the top expensive. A small car, easy to park a good run around for 8 days for two people plenty of room for two bags.
Got us to where we needed to be. We were picked up from the airport promptly and got on our way quickly. The driver knew how to avoid the traffic at the roundabout by the airport to get us to the depot.
Good value for money.
